{
  "texts": [
    "Li and Liu (2021) have employed a deep neural network (DNN) method for prediction by extracting valuable data as a feature with matching weights.",
    "The NNs architecture has used several updated hidden layers.",
    "These hidden layers were managed through feed forwarding and backpropagation data, which were generated by prior cases.",
    "The DNN algorithm has been suggested for several steps, including initialization and preprocessing of the data.",
    "The system was trained by using labeled data from a dataset in the training mode, and the system was tested in the testing mode."
  ]
}